name: 925 CRUCIFIX DAGGER WITH ROPE CHAIN
sort_details:
Crucifix Dagger in pendant form along with a 92.5 silver rope chain.

specification_name: ["In order to keep your jewellery looking fresh and new, we advise to keep your pieces dry and if they do come in contact with water to dry them immediately. Avoid letting your jewellery come in contact with sweat, perfumes, chlorine, nail polish remover, hair spray and soaps. Store your silver jewellery in airtight bags or in your HotNWatNot box. Silver tarnishes quickly when it\u2019s exposed to oxygen and sulphur. In order to avoid this we advise wearing your jewellery as often as possible as the oil from your skin prevents tarnishing. When you need to clean the silver pieces, use a jewellery cloth as the metal is soft."]
details: Our radiant crucifix dagger always catches the attention, especially with the finely crafted rope chain. Made from polished sterling silver! Look closely and you’ll see our '925 HNWN' signature lovingly engraved for you on the backside of the charm.

specification_name: ["In order to keep your jewellery looking fresh and new, we advise to keep your pieces dry and if they do come in contact with water to dry them immediately. Avoid letting your jewellery come in contact with sweat, perfumes, chlorine, nail polish remover, hair spray and soaps. Store your silver jewellery in airtight bags or in your HotNWatNot box.
